            <title>[LU-16775] Proper target cleanup in sanity-sec test_31</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16775</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanity-sec test_31 adds an LNet network tcp999, and associated &lt;tt&gt;servicenode&lt;/tt&gt; param on MDS target. This param must be cleared when exiting the test, otherwise it can lead to incorrect client HA behavior, trying to reach out to the fake service nodes.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
